ate, for now, despite President Donald Trump\u2019s call in his State of the Union speech that Republicans in Congress pass the bill \u201cbefore anything else.\u201d", "large_image": "7cZ9bpdM1LeY7UKk.png", "title": "Republican voter ID bill stalls in Senate despite Trump demands"}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASG09n4wK", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 50, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8451928, "raw_content": "There's never going to be a point where the grievance cultures stop trying to take wealth and power away from whoever they perceive to be \"too White.\"\n\nRight now at most 62-63% of the country is White if you include White Hispanics. I think for the most part Cubans and Argentinians do assimilate, but we're getting flooded with Muslims, Hindu nationalists and anti-White Latin Americans. The Irish and Italians came here legally and were forced to assimilate because net migration was never more than 3-4% of the total population per year. And that was at its PEAK. \n\nDEI & Wokeness aren't going away. I laugh when anti woke liberals and libertarians and moderates try to claim that the market is going to eventually fix this problem. No, you retards. These people don't care about customer service. They know they can use the power of the state, banks and woke billionaires to fund this stuff for the rest of time. ", "author": "HorrorGameDev", "created": 1772226657524, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Gnometard", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Guys and gals: this country is never going to get better unless demographic replacement is reversed. Ever. ", "last_comment_created": 1772230449350, "content": "<p>There's never going to be a point where the grievance cultures stop trying to take wealth and power away from whoever they perceive to be &quot;too White.&quot;</p>\n<p>Right now at most 62-63% of the country is White if you include White Hispanics. I think for the most part Cubans and Argentinians do assimilate, but we're getting flooded with Muslims, Hindu nationalists and anti-White Latin Americans. The Irish and Italians came here legally and were forced to assimilate because net migration was never more than 3-4% of the total population per year. And that was at its PEAK.</p>\n<p>DEI &amp; Wokeness aren't going away. I laugh when anti woke liberals and libertarians and moderates try to claim that the market is going to eventually fix this problem. No, you retards. These people don't care about customer service. They know they can use the power of the state, banks and woke billionaires to fund this stuff for the rest of time.</p>\n", "score_down": 1, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 12, "score_up": 51, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2026807115608699144", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASG0AtpES", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 26, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8452334, "raw_content": "", "author": "_Liberty_Prime_", "created": 1772239386427, "profile_picture": "evWxa80vv4JN", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "_Liberty_Prime_", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASG0AtpES.png", "removal_source": "", "lin